  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为船员转运流程画一个流程图。核心场景是：遇到天气延误时，怎么决定是等待还是改派下一班。起点应该是判断是否有天气延误。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c1",
        "Weather delay?"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，c1用菱形表示判断节点。那如果天气没问题，直接走正常流程？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c1",
        "c6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，c1判断为No的话，直接到c6完成船员转运。但如果c1是Yes，就要进入二级判断：延误时间是否超过本班次的剩余时间。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c1",
        "c2",
        "c6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我加上c2节点，标注为'延误是否超过班次时间'。然后c2分出两条路径：Yes走c3去港口，No走c5原地等待。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c2",
        "c3",
        "c5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，c3之后应该先到c4等待下一班次，然后再回到c1重新判断天气，不是直接转运。这个循环容易漏掉。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c3",
        "c4",
        "c1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我修正一下：c3到c4，c4再回到c1形成闭环。那c5等待延误结束后，也是到c6对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c3",
        "c4",
        "c1",
        "c5",
        "c6"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，c5直接连c6。整个逻辑就是：小延误等，大延误换班，换班后重新评估天气。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c5",
        "c6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "流程图画好了，用了base主题。我注意到节点文字里用了换行，比如'Weather\\ndelay?'和'Tranfer crew\\nto the system'，这样布局比较紧凑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c1",
        "c6",
        "theme"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "c6的Transfer拼错了，应该是Transfer不是Tranfer。另外c2的描述'Is delay longer than time in shift'可以更清楚一点，不过先这样吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c2",
        "c6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "修正了，c6现在标注为'Transfer crew to the system'。我检查一下所有连接：c1-No→c6，c1-Yes→c2-Yes→c3→c4→c1，c2-No→c5→c6。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c6",
        "c1",
        "c2",
        "c3",
        "c4",
        "c5"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后输出的时候，我们需要svg和png两种格式。png要宽2400像素，背景透明，方便放进报告里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "svg",
        "png",
        "port"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "搞定。用mmdc先导出crew_transfer.svg，再导出crew_transfer.png，参数是-w 2400 -b transparent。对了，svg导出后可能需要手动把<br改成<br/，这是已知的小问题。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "mmdc",
        "crew_transfer.mmd",
        "crew_transfer.svg",
        "crew_transfer.png"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
